title: At least six dead as Typhoon Mujigae hits southern China
text:
At least six dead as Typhoon Mujigae hits southern China 
Published By: Mashable - Today 
The typhoon that hit the Chinese shore on Sunday has killed at least six people and left dozens of fishermen missing, said local authorities...
